Web Socket Client for Chrome
--------------------------------------------------

A simple UI for a web socket client that can be used to manually test web socket endpoints.

1. Clone the repo.
2. Go to 'chrome://extensions'.
3. Check 'Developer Mode'.
4. Choose 'Load Unpacked Extension...'.
5. Browse to the location you downloaded the repo.
6. Open the client by client 'Options' underneath 'Web Socket Client' in 'chrome://extensions' or by clicking the 'WS Client' browser action to the right of your address bar.

This extension requires no permissions!